# Group Auth

Auth related endpoints.

## Login [/oauth2/token/]

### Request token [POST]

+ Request (application/x-www-form-urlencoded)
    + grant_type: password (string)
    + client_id: 20pXYRpXeicuPTU93Oc26rEMV1hcFCbyMXI7oct4 (string)
    + client_secret: 8EkFbvzeD0xSKszFh4n0bGGGuYzoQy979r4KnNlj0Avp4nQPrnMwSsEe5WVEx9EY4BTiIzIVb9XKYFpvI2tdzxB6ocY75ekXdT6nSuHZqLPU512fnqaUVgtXAII6rksn (string)
    + username: username (string)
    + password: pass (string)
    + Body

            grant_type=password&client_id=20pXYRpXeicuPTU93Oc26rEMV1hcFCbyMXI7oct4&username=username&password=pass&client_secret=8EkFbvzeD0xSKszFh4n0bGGGuYzoQy979r4KnNlj0Avp4nQPrnMwSsEe5WVEx9EY4BTiIzIVb9XKYFpvI2tdzxB6ocY75ekXdT6nSuHZqLPU512fnqaUVgtXAII6rksn

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (AuthToken)

+ Response 400
    + Attributes (StandardError)

+ Response 500
    + Attributes (StandardError)

