## Forgot password [/api/v1/forgot-password/]

### Forgot password [POST]

Sends email / SMS with reset password link.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + username: `user@test.com`
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200

+ Response 400
    + Attributes (StandardError)

+ Response 403
    + Attributes (StandardError)

+ Response 500
    + Attributes (StandardError)


## Set password [/api/v1/set-password/{access_key}/]

+ Parameters
    + access_key: `OUCErWl4DXJ0IsIobpIfYXJyfF7C9S` (string) - token received on forgot password request

### Set password [POST]

Changes user's password and deletes tokens.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + `new_password`: `passwd`
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200

+ Response 400
    + Attributes (StandardError)

+ Response 403
    + Attributes (StandardError)

+ Response 500
    + Attributes (StandardError)
